OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeak ScotRail fares to be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscrapped for six months    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Peak fares on ScotRail are to be       
OL,6, suspended for six months in a bid to   
OL,7, make train travel more affordable.     
OL,9,FThe pilot scheme will begin in April   
OL,10,Fnext year and will be subsidised by    
OL,11,F#15m from the Scottish government's    
OL,12,Flatest budget.                         
OL,14,FThe move will see the cost of some peak
OL,15,Fhour, or anytime, ScotRail fares nearly
OL,16,Fhalve.                                 
OL,18,FUnions and passenger groups have       
OL,19,Fwelcomed the plan as a way of coaxing  
OL,20,Fpeople back to the railways.           
